---
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="The Story Behind the Weinberger Reuben - Limerick's Sandwich Junction"
  description="Discover the history and inspiration behind one of our most beloved sandwiches."
>
  <!-- ARTICLE HERO -->
  <section
    class="relative h-96 md:h-[500px] w-full overflow-hidden bg-cover bg-center"
    style="background-image: url('https://images.pexels.com/photos/1633578/pexels-photo-1633578.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1600');"
  >
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-primary/50"></div>
  </section>

  <!-- ARTICLE CONTENT -->
  <article class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-background">
    <div class="container max-w-2xl">
      <!-- ARTICLE HEADER -->
      <header class="mb-12">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
          <span class="bg-accent/20 text-primary px-3 py-1 rounded text-sm font-bold">Story</span>
        </div>
        
        <h1 class="font-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-primary mb-4">
          The Story Behind the Weinberger Reuben
        </h1>

        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between gap-4 pb-6 border-b border-border/40">
          <div>
            <p class="text-foreground/70 mb-2">
              By <span class="font-bold text-primary">Chris Limerick</span>
            </p>
            <time class="text-foreground/60 text-sm">May 1, 2024</time>
          </div>
          <span class="text-foreground/60 text-sm">5 minute read</span>
        </div>
      </header>

      <!-- ARTICLE BODY -->
      <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none text-foreground/80 space-y-6 mb-12">
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
          When you walk into Limerick's Sandwich Junction and look at our menu, the Weinberger Reuben sits right at the top of our DELI section at $14.49. But this sandwich isn't just another item on a list—it's a piece of history, a tribute to tradition, and one of the most beloved creations we've ever had the honor of serving.
        </p>

        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
          The story begins in New York, where Reuben sandwiches have been a cornerstone of Jewish deli culture for over a century. But the Weinberger Reuben has its own Ennis, Texas chapter—one rooted in family recipes, local love, and the pursuit of perfection.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-primary mt-8 mb-4">
          The Ingredients of Tradition
        </h2>

        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
          The classic Reuben is simple in concept but demanding in execution. You need quality corned beef, fresh pastrami, Swiss cheese that actually melts, authentic Russian dressing, real sauerkraut (not the store-bought shortcut), and bread that can hold it all together. We use marble rye, grilled to golden perfection.
        </p>

        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
          But we didn't just follow tradition—we elevated it. Our corned beef is sourced locally when possible, brined and cooked in-house to ensure it's tender and flavorful. The pastrami brings a smoky note that rounds out the palate. The Russian dressing? That's our own recipe, balanced between mayo, ketchup, and spices to complement rather than overwhelm.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-primary mt-8 mb-4">
          Why the Reuben Belongs Here
        </h2>

        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
          You might wonder why a classic New York deli sandwich sits in the heart of Downtown Ennis, Texas. The answer is simple: great food transcends geography. When we opened Limerick's, we wanted to honor the great sandwich traditions from around the world—New Orleans, New York, Cuba, Italy, and more. These traditions converge here, in our little Junction.
        </p>

        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
          The Weinberger Reuben represents our commitment to authenticity and quality. It's a sandwich that demands respect, that takes time to make right, and that reminds you why sandwiches matter. Every layer has a purpose. Every ingredient has been chosen with care.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-primary mt-8 mb-4">
          From the Menu to Your Table
        </h2>

        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
          Today, the Weinberger Reuben is one of our signature items. It shows up on t-shirts, in customer reviews, and in the hearts of Ennis regulars who come back week after week for their fix. We've had customers tell us it's the best Reuben they've ever had—better than places in New York, Chicago, or any other deli hotspot.
        </p>

        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
          That's high praise, and it motivates us every single day. We make the Weinberger Reuben the same way we make every sandwich at Limerick's: with attention to detail, respect for the craft, and genuine care for the person who's about to enjoy it.
        </p>

        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed font-bold text-primary">
          The next time you bite into a Weinberger Reuben at Limerick's, you're not just eating a sandwich. You're tasting history, tradition, and the pride of a small-town deli that refuses to compromise on quality.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- SHARE & CALL TO ACTION -->
      <div class="bg-accent/5 rounded-lg p-8 border border-accent/30 mb-12">
        <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-primary text-lg mb-4">Try the Weinberger Reuben</h3>
        <p class="text-foreground/80 mb-6">
          Ready to experience the legend for yourself? Order online or stop by Limerick's today.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
          <a
            href="https://limerickssandwichjunction.smartonlineorder.com/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="inline-block px-6 py-3 bg-primary text-accent font-bold rounded hover:bg-primary/90 transition-all duration-300"
          >
            Order Online
          </a>
          <a
            href="tel:+19034051995"
            class="inline-block px-6 py-3 bg-secondary text-background font-bold rounded hover:bg-secondary/90 transition-all duration-300"
          >
            Call (903) 405-1995
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- BACK TO BLOG -->
      <div class="text-center">
        <a href="/blog" class="text-primary hover:underline font-bold">
          ← Back to Blog
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>

  <!-- RELATED POSTS -->
  <section class="bg-accent/5 py-16 md:py-20">
    <div class="container max-w-4xl">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl font-bold text-primary text-center mb-12">
        More Stories from the Junction
      </h2>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <!-- Related Post 1 -->
        <article class="bg-card rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300 border border-border/40">
          <div class="h-40 overflow-hidden bg-gray-200" style="background-image: url('https://images.pexels.com/photos/1640777/pexels-photo-1640777.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1200'); background-size: cover; background-position: center;">
            <img
              src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/1640777/pexels-photo-1640777.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1200"
              alt="Local sourcing"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <p class="text-secondary font-bold text-sm mb-2">Commitment</p>
            <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-primary text-lg mb-3 line-clamp-2">
              Why We Source Local: Our Commitment to Ennis
            </h3>
            <p class="text-foreground/70 text-sm mb-4 line-clamp-2">
              Learn about our commitment to supporting local suppliers and farmers...
            </p>
            <a
              href="#"
              class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-secondary text-background font-bold rounded text-sm hover:bg-secondary/90 transition-all duration-300"
            >
              Read More
            </a>
          </div>
        </article>

        <!-- Related Post 2 -->
        <article class="bg-card rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300 border border-border/40">
          <div class="h-40 overflow-hidden bg-gray-200" style="background-image: url('https://images.pexels.com/photos/1647164/pexels-photo-1647164.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=800'); background-size: cover; background-position: center;">
            <img
              src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/1647164/pexels-photo-1647164.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=800"
              alt="Muffuletta"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <p class="text-accent font-bold text-sm mb-2">Feature</p>
            <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-primary text-lg mb-3 line-clamp-2">
              Sandwich of the Month: The Muffuletta
            </h3>
            <p class="text-foreground/70 text-sm mb-4 line-clamp-2">
              A New Orleans classic lands in Downtown Ennis. Discover the flavors...
            </p>
            <a
              href="#"
              class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-primary text-accent font-bold rounded text-sm hover:bg-primary/90 transition-all duration-300"
            >
              Read More
            </a>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
